ternal text\" href=\"http://restaurant-ingthroughhistory.com/2011/11/15/dipping-into-the-finger-bowl/\">\"Dipping into the finger bowl\"</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2014-01-26</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Dipping+into+the+finger+bowl&amp;rft.date=2011-11-15&amp;rft.aulast=Whitaker&amp;rft.aufirst=Jan&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Frestaurant-ingthroughhistory.com%2F2011%2F11%2F15%2Fdipping-into-the-finger-bowl%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFinger+bowl\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Baldrige, Letitia (1990). <i>Letitia Baldrige's Complete Guide to the New Manners for the '90s</i>. New York: Rawson Associates. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-89256-320-6\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0-89256-320-6\">0-89256-320-6</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Letitia+Baldrige%27s+Complete+Guide+to+the+New+Manners+for+the+%2790s&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=Rawson+Associates&amp;rft.date=1990&amp;rft.isbn=0-89256-320-6&amp;rft.aulast=Baldrige&amp;rft.aufirst=Letitia&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFinger+bowl\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span><sup class=\"reference\" style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">:<span>146</span></sup></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"ht